Citation.sTitle: Viscosities, Densities, and Speeds of Sound of Binary Mixtures of o-Xylene, m-Xylene, p-Xylene, and Isopropylbenzene with 2-Butanone at 298.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: The viscosities, densities, and speeds of sound of binary mixtures of 2-butanone with o-xylene, m-xylene, p-xylene, and isopropylbenzene have been determined at 298.15 K over the whole composition range. Deviations in viscosity () and excess compressibility () were calculated.
